/ About me Section
.container
  %section#about.main-nav
    %h1
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-info-sign{"aria-hidden" => "true"}
      About
    .row
      .col-sm-4
        / My picture
        / <img src="http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/avatar.png" alt="description" title="tool tip" class="img-circle shadow up-hover avatar">
      .col-sm-8
        %h2.text-primary.stm-font Skills
        %p
          Full Stack Web Development
        %h2.text-primary.stm-font Tools
        %p Ruby, Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL - HTML, CSS, SCSS, Bootstrap - JavaScript, jQuery, React.js, PostgreSQL - Git, Heroku
  %section#portfolio.main-nav
    / start portfolio
    %h1
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-book{"aria-hidden" => "true"}
      Portfolio
    .row
      / -start row
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 1
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/simon.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/QbRyqq"}
              %h3.stm-font Simon Game
            %p An emulation of the classic memory game using jQuery. Graphics are pure CSS. It'uses the new AudioContext API, so you need an up-to-date version of firefox or chrome to run it.
      / end element 1
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 2
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/pomo.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/vObzWm"}
              %h3.stm-font Pomodoro Clock
            %p A timer to help you to improve your skills. Made with simple CSS, and jQuery. The vector arts are made by me in Inkscape
      / end element 2
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 3
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/calc.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/OVabRP"}
              %h3.stm-font Pocket Calculator
            %p A bootstrap and jQuery powered emulation of a vintage pocket calculator. It features the classic operator chaining workflow, and the percent operator in windows calc mode.
      / end element 3
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 4
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/quotes.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/jPQqwB"}
              %h3.stm-font Random Quotes Machine
            %p This little app retrieves random quotes from the 'Quotes.net' servers. It uses AJAX calls in jQuery, and the Twitter API. Made with Bootstrap, and custom images
      / end element 4
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 5
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/cnews.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/WvPNPM"}
              %h3.stm-font fcc Camper News
            %p This app use Ajax to obtain infos about the last posts on the 'freeCodeCamp.com' forum. Then it displays the data using the powerful Bootstrap's responsive grid. Powered by jQuery.
      / end element 5
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        / start element 6
        .thumbnail.shadow.up-hover
          %img{:src => "http://Kenia.altervista.org/ext/tic.jpg"}/
          .cust-caption
            %a{:href => "http://codepen.io/Em-Ant/full/KpEWdR"}
              %h3.stm-font Tic Tac Toe
            %p The access point to understanding AI in games. The computer player uses the classic MiniMax algorithm. Try to beat him if you can. Made in Bootstrap, jQuery and font Awesome.
      / end element 6
    / -end row
  / end portfolio
/ end container
